{
  "texts": [
    "In this way, our recognition system combines (2) the advantages of two different modalities and thus is more robust against noise residing in a single modality.",
    "Furthermore, we adopt a sign detection method to localise signs appearing in the video.",
    "It removes redundancy in the input videos, thereby significantly improving the accuracy of sign language recognition.",
    "We implement data normalisation to standardise input data, enhancing our algorithm's robustness across diverse photographic conditions.",
    "Image enhancement techniques are applied, such as histogram equalization, to mitigate the impact of the environment on the user-input videos."
  ]
}